---
export const prerender = true;

import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = "June 21, 2025";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — InstaDownloader"
  description="Read InstaDownloader's privacy policy. We are committed to protecting your privacy. Learn how we collect, use, and safeguard your information."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-24 pb-16 min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero Banner -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-16 sm:py-20">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[300px] rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-20"
          style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse, var(--color-brand-mid), transparent 70%)"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass-card text-sm font-medium text-text-secondary mb-6">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-mid" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
          Last updated: {lastUpdated}
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4">
          <span class="gradient-text">Privacy</span> <span class="text-text-primary">Policy</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Your privacy matters to us. This policy explains how InstaDownloader handles your information when you use our free Instagram downloading service.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="glass-card p-8 sm:p-12 space-y-10 policy-content">

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>InstaDownloader is designed with privacy in mind. We collect minimal information necessary to provide our service:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Anonymous analytics data including pages visited, time spent on pages, and general geographic region (country level).</li>
            <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> Browser type, device type, and operating system for service optimization purposes.</li>
            <li><strong>URLs Submitted:</strong> Instagram URLs you paste into our downloader are processed in real-time and are not stored on our servers after processing.</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="info-box">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
            <span>We do <strong>not</strong> collect your name, email address, phone number, or any personal identifying information.</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>The limited data we collect is used solely to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide and improve our Instagram downloading service</li>
            <li>Analyze usage patterns to enhance user experience</li>
            <li>Ensure service stability and performance</li>
            <li>Protect against abuse, spam, and malicious activity</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or share your data with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>3. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
          <p>We use minimal cookies to ensure proper functionality of our website:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Preference Cookies:</strong> Store your theme preference (dark/light mode).</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Anonymous analytics to understand how users interact with the site (e.g., Google Analytics with IP anonymization enabled).</li>
          </ul>
          <p>You can disable cookies in your browser settings. Note that disabling cookies may affect theme preferences and some site functionality.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>Our service may integrate with third-party services for analytics and performance. These include:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Anonymous usage statistics. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Privacy Policy →</a></li>
            <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> CDN and DDoS protection. <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare Privacy Policy →</a></li>
          </ul>
          <p>InstaDownloader is not affiliated with Instagram or Meta Platforms, Inc. All Instagram content remains the property of its respective creators and copyright holders.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>We retain anonymized usage data for up to 26 months to identify trends and improve the service. Individual URL submissions are processed in memory and are never written to permanent storage.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>Since we do not collect personal data, there is typically no personal data to access, correct, or delete. However, you have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Opt out of Google Analytics by using the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a></li>
            <li>Clear cookies from your browser at any time</li>
            <li>Contact us with any privacy-related concerns</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>InstaDownloader is not directed at children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect any information from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided us with information, please contact us immediately.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
          <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>. We aim to respond to all inquiries within 48 hours.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .policy-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-brand-start), var(--color-brand-mid));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .policy-section {
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .policy-section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .policy-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .policy-content ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
    space-y: 0.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .policy-content ul li {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .policy-content ul li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-brand-mid);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .policy-content a {
    color: var(--color-brand-mid);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .policy-content a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .policy-content strong {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .info-box {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.2);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .info-box svg {
    color: var(--color-brand-mid);
    margin-top: 1px;
  }
</style>
